EN: They hold hands and swing together.

ZH: 我们在花园里摆动秋千。
EN: We swing on the swing in the garden.

ZH: 风吹得树枝摆动不已。
EN: The wind blew the branches back and forth.

ZH: 她坐在椅子上摆动脚。
EN: She sits and swings her feet on the chair.

